---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SideDrawer from '../components/SideDrawer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About SPS | The Legacy of Intelligent Security" description="Tracing the evolution of SPS from a 1965 guard force to India's premier Security Intelligence Platform.">
  <SideDrawer />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="brutalist-section pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-compliance uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Our Heritage</span>
          <h1 class="text-heading-1 text-primary-accent mb-6">THE QUIET PROFESSIONAL</h1>
          <p class="text-2xl text-body font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">
            For sixty years, we have stood watch. Now, we speak.
          </p>
          <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-neutral-300">
            <p>
              Security, at its apex, is invisible. It is the incident that never occurred; the breach that was preempted; the crisis that was managed in silence. Since 1965, as a <strong>Sukhi Enterprise</strong>, SPS has operated on this principle of quiet competence.
            </p>
            <p>
              We began by securing the physical perimeter. Today, we secure the informational one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Stats Card -->
        <div class="brutalist-card brutalist-card--verified p-12 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-6xl font-black text-primary-accent font-mono">1965</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-3">Established</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-6xl font-black text-success font-mono">10</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-3">Verticals</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-2 border-t border-neutral-700 pt-8">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-compliance font-mono">ISO 9001:2015</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-3">Certified Excellence</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Mission Narrative -->
  <section class="brutalist-section brutalist-section--dark py-24">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="text-heading-2 text-white">THE EVOLUTION OF THREAT</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 prose prose-invert prose-xl">
        <p class="lead text-2xl text-white font-light">
          The threat landscape of 2026 bears little resemblance to that of 1965.
        </p>
        <p>
          In the mid-20th century, security was defined by gates, guards, and physical barriers. The adversary was tangible. Today, the adversary is often formlessâ€”a line of code, a fraudulent digital identity, or a regulatory oversight.
        </p>
        <p>
          SPS evolved to meet this reality. We transitioned from being solely a provider of manpower to becoming a provider of <strong>intelligence</strong>. We recognised that in the information age, the most potent weapon is accurate, timely knowledge.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is to democratise this high-level security intelligence. We believe that a jewellery showroom in Zaveri Bazaar deserves the same quality of threat assessment as a multinational corporation in Bandra-Kurla Complex.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Sukhi Standard -->
  <section class="brutalist-section py-24">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-heading-2 mb-12">THE SUKHI STANDARD</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div class="group">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-compliance mb-4 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">01. Absolute Integrity</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
              We do not compromise. Our protocols are rigorous, our compliance is absolute, and our word is our bond. In an industry often plagued by opacity, we offer radical transparency.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-success mb-4 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">02. Intelligence-Led</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
              We do not react; we anticipate. Every guard deployed, every camera installed, and every protocol written is derived from data-driven threat analysis.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-accent mb-4 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">03. Client Sovereignty</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
              We view security not as a cost centre, but as a business enabler. Our goal is to secure your environment so seamlessly that you are free to focus entirely on your enterprise.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-critical mb-4 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">04. Continuous Evolution</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
              The methods of 1965 do not solve the problems of 2026. We are in a state of constant learning, adapting our tradecraft to counter emerging threats.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
